but you said the handbook
must be kept a secret.

26
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,900
[Dreamlike Past]

27
00:02:30,950 --> 00:02:32,950
[Health Examination Report]

28
00:02:50,170 --> 00:02:51,520
Ageing?

29
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,680
Exhaustion?

30
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,160
Seriously?

31
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:05,770
Such an old-fashioned story for this era.

32
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,450
Mr Xu.

33
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:35,480
You told me to take out your collections

34
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,690
just to give them all to Ruyi Pavilion?

35
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,480
Ask Lawyer Wu to come here later.

36
00:03:43,410 --> 00:03:44,410
I'm making a will.

37
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:45,980
Mr Xu.

38
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:49,400
You'll find a better doctor to cure you.

39
00:03:51,690 --> 00:03:52,820
To be able to meet her

40
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,329
is far more than I could ask.

41
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:57,440
Are you sure to leave all your assets

42
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,640
to Ms Qiao?

43
00:03:59,350 --> 00:04:00,410
Don't ask anymore.

44
00:04:00,890 --> 00:04:01,810
Do it now.

45
00:04:08,550 --> 00:04:12,840
[Inpatient Rehabilitation Building]

46
00:04:27,930 --> 00:04:29,320
What brings you here?

47
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,080
What do you think?

48
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:33,080
Qi Xiao Ba told us

49
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,800
that you have severe peanut allergies.

50
00:04:36,330 --> 00:04:37,720
We're here to visit you.

51
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:41,490
He could've just tricked Xu Jin alone.
But he got you here too?

52
00:04:41,490 --> 00:04:44,220
You're still thinking
about Xu Jin in this state?

53
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,640
I really shouldn't have helped you.

54
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,240
You have the nerve to show up?

55
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,390
Xu Jin.

56
00:05:03,490 --> 00:05:04,860
Where are your manners?

57
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,320
Wait, wait for me.

58
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,650
Why did you hold me back?

59
00:05:09,650 --> 00:05:10,980
You'd better stay here.

60
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,370
Let them sort it out.

61
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,130
It's my fault for lying.

62
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,920
But I like you and that's true.

63
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,120
Since a very long time ago.

64
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,850
I have this dream.

65
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,380
In the dream, I lived in the ancient time.

66
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,280
I had a great husband.

67
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,130
And he looked exactly like you.

68
00:05:41,450 --> 00:05:43,380
I've been waiting for that person.

69
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,360
Everyone around me thinks I'm crazy.

70
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,120
But you came at last.

71
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,320
I didn't know

72
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:53,100
the reason you were
blowing hot and cold before.

73
00:05:55,010 --> 00:05:56,360
But I finally did

74
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,600
on the day before yesterday.

75
00:06:00,730 --> 00:06:02,520
What happened to your body?

76
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,840
What did you see?

77
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,660
Your health examination report.

78
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,360
And our photo.

79
00:06:13,570 --> 00:06:14,630
I've told you this.

80
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:19,120
Don't enter my study
room without permission.

81
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,880
You've broken the agreement.

82
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:23,120
Don't bring that up now.

83
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:25,800
If you don't like me,
why would you marry me?

84
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,970
Or keep our photo?

85
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,120
Or come here?

86
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:32,690
Make Dreamlike Past Exhibition a success.

87
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,010
On December 25th,

88
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,650
we'll get a divorce.

89
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:44,860
I'll wait at the amusement park on
Christmas Eve until you show up.

90
00:06:51,330 --> 00:06:53,680
[Hi, I'm your old friend, Uncle San.]

91
00:06:54,090 --> 00:06:56,420
[Today is December 24th. Christmas Eve.]

92
00:06:56,880 --> 00:07:00,000
[I believe you may be on your
way to see your loved one,]

93
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:03,040
[or going on a long-anticipated date .]

94
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,180
[But I've always thought]

95
00:07:05,210 --> 00:07:06,270
[that to all of us,]

96
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:08,530
[it's not the festival that matters,]

97
00:07:08,530 --> 00:07:10,730
[instead, it's the person beside you.]

98
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,000
[And of course,]

99
00:07:12,050 --> 00:07:14,510
[there'll be news on
exhibitions as usual.]

100
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:18,720
[Firstly, the Dreamlike Past
Exhibition I've been waiting for]

101
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,480
[has started today at Ruyi Pavilion.]

102
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,740
[I heard it's been very well-received.]

103
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,050
[The exhibition lasts for 20 days.]

104
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,080
[Don't miss out.]

105
00:07:47,450 --> 00:07:49,520
[Marriage Termination Agreement]

106
00:07:51,170 --> 00:07:52,050
Xu Jin.

107
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,280
What is this?

108
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,260
I waited for hours,
and this is what I got?

109
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:04,740
It's just an illness.
I can stay by your side.

110
00:08:09,810 --> 00:08:10,760
You said

111
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,720
that you dreamed about
us in the ancient times.

112
00:08:17,290 --> 00:08:18,290
To you,

113
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:19,970
it's a dream.

114
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,370
But to me, it was real.

115
00:08:24,450 --> 00:08:27,650
I've been waiting and
protecting it for a thousand years.

116
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,090
What?

117
00:08:30,030 --> 00:08:30,970
Rong'er.

118
00:08:33,490 --> 00:08:34,640
This is all I asked.

119
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,799
[You can share my luck.]

120
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,860
The agreement's in your hand.

121
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:35,560
Do whatever you want with it.

122
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:42,310
Cancelled.

123
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:48,280
I mean, we shouldn't be separated anymore.

124
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,600
Make everyday spent together count.

125
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:55,060
You got what you asked for, but I haven't.
How could you do this?

126
