[On March 2017, "The Blooms of
RUYI Pavilion" was officially launched.]

127
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:54,100
[On September 2019, the filming of
"The Blooms of RUYI Pavilion"began.]

128
00:10:54,190 --> 00:10:57,320
[Countless script postponements
in the two years of scriptwriting.]

129
00:10:57,400 --> 00:11:00,350
[There were regrets and shortcomings,
but we tried our best.]

130
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,840
[Thank you for staying till
the end with love and tolerance.]

131
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:05,810
[Love is about being around.
Thank you for being with us.]

132
00:11:05,890 --> 00:11:08,270
[From the crew of
"The Blooms At RUYI Pavilion"]

133
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,890
[If... you would ask for more,]

134
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:14,260
[here's another bonus scene.]

135
00:11:14,350 --> 00:11:20,480
[Thanks to all viewers
for truly loving "Little RUYI".]

136
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,020
[Mr Xu.]

137
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,730
[The doctor said, your bodily
functions decline continuously.]

138
00:11:28,730 --> 00:11:29,960
[You needed more check-ups.]

139
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,090
[If this goes on...]

140
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:32,010
No need.

141
00:11:33,860 --> 00:11:36,950
[Qiao Yi Rong sent a Friend Request]

142
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:40,560
[Friend Request accepted.
Let's chat now.]

143
00:11:45,420 --> 00:11:51,220
[Friend Request accepted.
Let's chat now.]

144
00:11:57,880 --> 00:12:01,080
Isn't sending a voice message
at night kind of frivolous?

145
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:12,920
[Hi, Mr Xu.]

146
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:14,690
[I'm Qiao Yi Rong.]

147
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:15,700
[Mr Xu.]

148
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,400
[I asked for your number]

149
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,250
[from Mr Ge.]

150
00:12:19,540 --> 00:12:21,250
[Hope I'm not disturbing.]

151
00:12:22,010 --> 00:12:25,000
[It's always been my wish to meet you.]

152
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:27,660
[But I didn't get the chance to do so]

153
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:29,390
[as you've been busy.]

154
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:35,000
[Ruyi Pavilion performed
poorly before this.]

155
00:12:35,940 --> 00:12:37,780
[If Dayu Auction House]

156
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:39,230
[hadn't contacted us,]

157
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:42,000
[and let us hold all the antique fairs,]

158
00:12:42,510 --> 00:12:45,110
[we would've closed down by now.]

159
00:12:45,810 --> 00:12:47,330
[Thank you very much.]

160
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:49,670
[Mr Xu.]

161
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:52,100
[Am I blurting things out?]

162
00:13:04,970 --> 00:13:07,890
[I received a very unique
antique hairpin today.]

163
00:13:08,180 --> 00:13:09,840
[Too bad I can't share it yet.]

164
00:13:09,870 --> 00:13:12,080
[Here's a selfie to remember this.]

165
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:15,470
[Should I make a video call?]

166
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:21,750
[Xu Jin]

167
00:13:29,540 --> 00:13:32,940
Mr Xu, that's too casual.

168
00:13:34,060 --> 00:13:35,770
I saw nothing.

169
00:13:37,510 --> 00:13:39,440
[Is anything the matter, Ms Qiao?]

170
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,880
Well...

171
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:49,010
We might need to discuss the reparation

172
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:50,870
